The WHOOZ mapping project aims to identify zones of overlapping usage between human and animal populations.\ \ The WHOOZ map does not attempt to accurately map animal populations, but rather the sites and spaces in which humans interact with animals. In a sense the mappers are mapping themselves as they interact with animals. \ \ Ultimately we hope the project will increase awareness among humans of the other inhabitants of this beautiful park.}
